          {
            "field_id": "google_forms:01:entry_554385011:190af230e7f4",
            "label": "What would be the results if funding is not received?",
            "help_text": null,
            "field_type": "textarea",
            "required": true,
            "options": null,
            "is_constituent_info": false,
            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* Erosion of U.S. preeminence in space science as China expands its lunar and Mars exploration capabilities\n* Risk of further layoffs and talent loss in the aerospace industrial base, specifically affecting commercial lunar partners\n* Inability to meet Decadal Survey milestones for critical missions in planetary defense and climate research\n* Long-term damage to the STEM talent pipeline and domestic aerospace workforce stability",
